channel.title: Project Annihilation |459| *Aug. 1st Update*
channel.description:
100% to S Quare Quxx & Brown. (I DID GET S Quare Quxx's APPROVAL)
[size=13pt][u]Update:[/u][/size] New Client Released.(Signature) More Bugs Fixed
[size=13pt][u]OLD Update:[/u][/size] Ancient ice spells now work! Range has been improved! More bugs fixed. [u]Some preview videos[/u]: (100% Brown) http://tinypic.com/player.php?v=2me7n83&s=3 Luring. http://tinypic.com/player.php?v=346rzgk&s=3 Some random death match. http://tinypic.com/player.php?v=vmrrlj&s=3 Dueling.
[size=12pt][u]Older Updates:[/u][/size] 100% Prayer, and Duel Arena released! [img]http://img41.imageshack.us/img41/5804/duelarenacopy.jpg[/img] [img]http://img41.yfrog.com/img41/1416/prayercopy.jpg[/img]
[center][size=20pt]Project Annihilation![/size] [img]http://i41.tinypic.com/2wganib.jpg[/img][/center]
Annihilation is the latest server being developed by Brown and S Quare Quxx. Unlike other servers going around this is a 459 server meaning it is based on the time of RuneScape when dragonfire shield was introduced, meaning no god wars or bounty hunter. The server is currently in beta stages but is being developed rapidly. [center] Skills:
[ul][*]Fletching. 100% [*]Runecrafting. 100% [*]Crafting. Near 100% [*]Mining. Near 100% [*]Smithing. 100%[/ul]
Minigames:
[ul][*]Dueling 100%[/ul]
[/center]
The server prides itself on having everything as near to 100% as possible with no bugs, because of this we will spend time on making features.
Annihilation also has close to 100% combat, we have spent numerous hours watching hundreds of PKing video's around this runescape time and have perfected our PVP timers, bonus's and everything else PVP. [center] First PKing video (PVP needs fixing): [url=http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2ELnfoCEpqw]http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2ELnfoCEpqw[/url] [/center] [u]Media[/u]: [IMG]http://i41.tinypic.com/qsp00h.png[/img] [IMG]http://i43.tinypic.com/2m44orq.jpg[/img] [IMG]http://i44.tinypic.com/2ce15py.png[/img] [IMG]http://i43.tinypic.com/x40upg.png[/img] [IMG]http://whipscape.jouluserver.com/upload/uploads/7401153_hitmasks2.png[/img] [IMG]http://i39.tinypic.com/2v8smco.png[/img] [IMG]http://i43.tinypic.com/2i0asuu.png[/img] [IMG]http://i26.tinypic.com/okue88.png[/img] [IMG]http://i27.tinypic.com/24ycwmb.jpg[/img] [IMG]http://whipscape.jouluserver.com/upload/uploads/9830593_PAGlobalObjects.png[/img]
...and much more, see you there.
[QUOTE=S Quare Quxx]Feel free to...[/QUOTE]
